705388f-c.title: Brooklyn: Lake Place - 6th Street (West)
705388f-c.text:
125 Lake Place, at the N.E. corcer of West 6th Street, showing one of
the many old one family homes that are fast disappearing in Brooklyn.
This set of three views were taken at the same time and exdlusive of No. 3
(which shows West 6th Street) are identical.
April 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
